{
  "video_id": "1BXYSGepx7Q",
  "title": "What you need to know about CRISPR | Ellen Jorgensen",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12850.0,
      "end_time": 15883.0,
      "text": "So, has everybody heard of CRISPR?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15883.0,
      "end_time": 18509.0,
      "text": "I would be shocked if you hadn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18509.0,
      "end_time": 21735.0,
      "text": "This is a technology -- it&#39;s for genome editing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21735.0,
      "end_time": 24593.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s so versatile and so controversial"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24593.0,
      "end_time": 28631.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s sparking all sorts of really interesting conversations."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28631.0,
      "end_time": 31281.0,
      "text": "Should we bring back the woolly mammoth?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31281.0,
      "end_time": 34041.0,
      "text": "Should we edit a human embryo?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34041.0,
      "end_time": 36997.0,
      "text": "And my personal favorite:"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36997.0,
      "end_time": 40672.0,
      "text": "How can we justify wiping out an entire species"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40672.0,
      "end_time": 43140.0,
      "text": "that we consider harmful to humans"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43140.0,
      "end_time": 44466.0,
      "text": "off the face of the Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44466.0,
      "end_time": 47165.0,
      "text": "using this technology?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47165.0,
      "end_time": 50472.0,
      "text": "This type of science is moving much faster"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50472.0,
      "end_time": 53340.0,
      "text": "than the regulatory mechanisms that govern it."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53340.0,
      "end_time": 55431.0,
      "text": "And so, for the past six years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55431.0,
      "end_time": 57863.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve made it my personal mission"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57863.0,
      "end_time": 60897.0,
      "text": "to make sure that as many people as possible understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60897.0,
      "end_time": 64021.0,
      "text": "these types of technologies and their implications."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64021.0,
      "end_time": 69089.0,
      "text": "Now, CRISPR has been the subject of a huge media hype,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69089.0,
      "end_time": 74337.0,
      "text": "and the words that are used most often are &quot;easy&quot; and &quot;cheap.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74337.0,
      "end_time": 77500.0,
      "text": "So what I want to do is drill down a little bit deeper"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77500.0,
      "end_time": 82954.0,
      "text": "and look into some of the myths and the realities around CRISPR."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82954.0,
      "end_time": 85594.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re trying to CRISPR a genome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 85594.0,
      "end_time": 89098.0,
      "text": "the first thing that you have to do is damage the DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89098.0,
      "end_time": 92164.0,
      "text": "The damage comes in the form of a double-strand break"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 92164.0,
      "end_time": 93752.0,
      "text": "through the double helix."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 93752.0,
      "end_time": 97088.0,
      "text": "And then the cellular repair processes kick in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97088.0,
      "end_time": 99751.0,
      "text": "and then we convince those repair processes"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 99751.0,
      "end_time": 102054.0,
      "text": "to make the edit that we want,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102054.0,
      "end_time": 103620.0,
      "text": "and not a natural edit."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103620.0,
      "end_time": 105929.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s how it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105929.0,
      "end_time": 107676.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a two-part system."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107676.0,
      "end_time": 111071.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve got a Cas9 protein and something called a guide RNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111071.0,
      "end_time": 113557.0,
      "text": "I like to think of it as a guided missile."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113557.0,
      "end_time": 116227.0,
      "text": "So the Cas9 -- I love to anthropomorphize --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116227.0,
      "end_time": 119481.0,
      "text": "so the Cas9 is kind of this Pac-Man thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 119481.0,
      "end_time": 121050.0,
      "text": "that wants to chew DNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121050.0,
      "end_time": 125230.0,
      "text": "and the guide RNA is the leash that&#39;s keeping it out of the genome"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 125230.0,
      "end_time": 128912.0,
      "text": "until it finds the exact spot where it matches."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 128912.0,
      "end_time": 131830.0,
      "text": "And the combination of those two is called CRISPR."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 131830.0,
      "end_time": 133422.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a system that we stole"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 133422.0,
      "end_time": 137469.0,
      "text": "from an ancient, ancient bacterial immune system."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 137469.0,
      "end_time": 142041.0,
      "text": "The part that&#39;s amazing about it is that the guide RNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 142041.0,
      "end_time": 143956.0,
      "text": "only 20 letters of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143956.0,
      "end_time": 146570.0,
      "text": "are what target the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 146570.0,
      "end_time": 148737.0,
      "text": "This is really easy to design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 148737.0,
      "end_time": 150985.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s really cheap to buy."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 150985.0,
      "end_time": 155014.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s the part that is modular in the system;"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 155014.0,
      "end_time": 157481.0,
      "text": "everything else stays the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 157481.0,
      "end_time": 162047.0,
      "text": "This makes it a remarkably easy and powerful system to use."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 162047.0,
      "end_time": 166311.0,
      "text": "The guide RNA and the Cas9 protein complex together"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 166311.0,
      "end_time": 168267.0,
      "text": "go bouncing along the genome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 168267.0,
      "end_time": 171784.0,
      "text": "and when they find a spot where the guide RNA matches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 171784.0,
      "end_time": 174663.0,
      "text": "then it inserts between the two strands of the double helix,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 174663.0,
      "end_time": 176692.0,
      "text": "it rips them apart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 176692.0,
      "end_time": 179962.0,
      "text": "that triggers the Cas9 protein to cut,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 179962.0,
      "end_time": 181816.0,
      "text": "and all of a sudden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 181816.0,
      "end_time": 183740.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve got a cell that&#39;s in total panic"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 183740.0,
      "end_time": 187000.0,
      "text": "because now it&#39;s got a piece of DNA that&#39;s broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 187000.0,
      "end_time": 188320.0,
      "text": "What does it do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 188320.0,
      "end_time": 190959.0,
      "text": "It calls its first responders."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 190959.0,
      "end_time": 193605.0,
      "text": "There are two major repair pathways."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 193605.0,
      "end_time": 198698.0,
      "text": "The first just takes the DNA and shoves the two pieces back together."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 198698.0,
      "end_time": 200820.0,
      "text": "This isn&#39;t a very efficient system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 200820.0,
      "end_time": 203573.0,
      "text": "because what happens is sometimes a base drops out"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 203573.0,
      "end_time": 205024.0,
      "text": "or a base is added."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 205024.0,
      "end_time": 208841.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an OK way to maybe, like, knock out a gene,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 208841.0,
      "end_time": 212098.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s not the way that we really want to do genome editing."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 212098.0,
      "end_time": 215017.0,
      "text": "The second repair pathway is a lot more interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 215017.0,
      "end_time": 216677.0,
      "text": "In this repair pathway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 216677.0,
      "end_time": 219382.0,
      "text": "it takes a homologous piece of DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 219382.0,
      "end_time": 222046.0,
      "text": "And now mind you, in a diploid organism like people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 222046.0,
      "end_time": 226318.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve got one copy of our genome from our mom and one from our dad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 226318.0,
      "end_time": 227617.0,
      "text": "so if one gets damaged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 227617.0,
      "end_time": 230036.0,
      "text": "it can use the other chromosome to repair it."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 230036.0,
      "end_time": 232518.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s where this comes from."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 232518.0,
      "end_time": 234006.0,
      "text": "The repair is made,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 234006.0,
      "end_time": 236616.0,
      "text": "and now the genome is safe again."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 236616.0,
      "end_time": 238497.0,
      "text": "The way that we can hijack this"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 238497.0,
      "end_time": 242229.0,
      "text": "is we can feed it a false piece of DNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 242229.0,
      "end_time": 244397.0,
      "text": "a piece that has homology on both ends"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 244397.0,
      "end_time": 246120.0,
      "text": "but is different in the middle."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 246120.0,
      "end_time": 248611.0,
      "text": "So now, you can put whatever you want in the center"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 248611.0,
      "end_time": 250150.0,
      "text": "and the cell gets fooled."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 250150.0,
      "end_time": 252293.0,
      "text": "So you can change a letter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 252293.0,
      "end_time": 253582.0,
      "text": "you can take letters out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 253582.0,
      "end_time": 256530.0,
      "text": "but most importantly, you can stuff new DNA in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 256529.99999999997,
      "end_time": 259088.99999999997,
      "text": "kind of like a Trojan horse."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 259089.0,
      "end_time": 261298.0,
      "text": "CRISPR is going to be amazing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 261298.0,
      "end_time": 264940.0,
      "text": "in terms of the number of different scientific advances"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 264940.0,
      "end_time": 266621.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s going to catalyze."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 266621.0,
      "end_time": 269866.0,
      "text": "The thing that&#39;s special about it is this modular targeting system."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 269866.0,
      "end_time": 273657.0,
      "text": "I mean, we&#39;ve been shoving DNA into organisms for years, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 273657.0,
      "end_time": 275808.0,
      "text": "But because of the modular targeting system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 275808.0,
      "end_time": 279423.0,
      "text": "we can actually put it exactly where we want it."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 279423.0,
      "end_time": 285116.0,
      "text": "The thing is that there&#39;s a lot of talk about it being cheap"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 285116.0,
      "end_time": 286882.0,
      "text": "and it being easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 286882.0,
      "end_time": 290242.0,
      "text": "And I run a community lab."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 290242.0,
      "end_time": 293822.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m starting to get emails from people that say stuff like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 293822.0,
      "end_time": 296243.0,
      "text": "&quot;Hey, can I come to your open night"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 296243.0,
      "end_time": 299884.0,
      "text": "and, like, maybe use CRISPR and engineer my genome?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 299884.0,
      "end_time": 301018.0,
      "text": "(Laugher)"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 301018.0,
      "end_time": 303376.0,
      "text": "Like, seriously."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 303376.0,
      "end_time": 305203.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m, &quot;No, you can&#39;t.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 305203.0,
      "end_time": 306237.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 306237.0,
      "end_time": 308616.0,
      "text": "&quot;But I&#39;ve heard it&#39;s cheap. I&#39;ve heard it&#39;s easy.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 308616.0,
      "end_time": 310823.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to explore that a little bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 310823.0,
      "end_time": 312796.0,
      "text": "So, how cheap is it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 312796.0,
      "end_time": 315665.0,
      "text": "Yeah, it is cheap in comparison."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 315665.0,
      "end_time": 319308.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s going to take the cost of the average materials for an experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 319308.0,
      "end_time": 321864.0,
      "text": "from thousands of dollars to hundreds of dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 321864.0,
      "end_time": 323824.0,
      "text": "and it cuts the time a lot, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 323824.0,
      "end_time": 326246.0,
      "text": "It can cut it from weeks to days."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 326246.0,
      "end_time": 327762.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s great."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 327762.0,
      "end_time": 330476.0,
      "text": "You still need a professional lab to do the work in;"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 330476.0,
      "end_time": 334012.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re not going to do anything meaningful outside of a professional lab."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 334012.0,
      "end_time": 336040.0,
      "text": "I mean, don&#39;t listen to anyone who says"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 336040.0,
      "end_time": 339421.0,
      "text": "you can do this sort of stuff on your kitchen table."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 339421.0,
      "end_time": 343953.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really not easy to do this kind of work."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 343953.0,
      "end_time": 346285.0,
      "text": "Not to mention, there&#39;s a patent battle going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 346285.0,
      "end_time": 348135.0,
      "text": "so even if you do invent something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 348135.0,
      "end_time": 354795.0,
      "text": "the Broad Institute and UC Berkeley are in this incredible patent battle."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 354795.0,
      "end_time": 357207.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really fascinating to watch it happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 357207.0,
      "end_time": 360479.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re accusing each other of fraudulent claims"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 360479.0,
      "end_time": 362234.0,
      "text": "and then they&#39;ve got people saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 362234.0,
      "end_time": 365042.0,
      "text": "&quot;Oh, well, I signed my notebook here or there.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 365042.0,
      "end_time": 367167.0,
      "text": "This isn&#39;t going to be settled for years."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 367167.0,
      "end_time": 368351.0,
      "text": "And when it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 368351.0,
      "end_time": 371660.0,
      "text": "you can bet you&#39;re going to pay someone a really hefty licensing fee"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 371660.0,
      "end_time": 373343.0,
      "text": "in order to use this stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 373343.0,
      "end_time": 375148.0,
      "text": "So, is it really cheap?"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 375148.0,
      "end_time": 381220.0,
      "text": "Well, it&#39;s cheap if you&#39;re doing basic research and you&#39;ve got a lab."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 381220.0,
      "end_time": 384417.0,
      "text": "How about easy? Let&#39;s look at that claim."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 384417.0,
      "end_time": 387881.0,
      "text": "The devil is always in the details."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 387881.0,
      "end_time": 391036.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t really know that much about cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 391036.0,
      "end_time": 392730.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re still kind of black boxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 392730.0,
      "end_time": 397614.0,
      "text": "For example, we don&#39;t know why some guide RNAs work really well"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 397614.0,
      "end_time": 399701.0,
      "text": "and some guide RNAs don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 399701.0,
      "end_time": 403193.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t know why some cells want to do one repair pathway"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 403193.0,
      "end_time": 406270.0,
      "text": "and some cells would rather do the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 406270.0,
      "end_time": 407578.0,
      "text": "And besides that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 407578.0,
      "end_time": 410471.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s the whole problem of getting the system into the cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 410471.0,
      "end_time": 411759.0,
      "text": "in the first place."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 411759.0,
      "end_time": 413785.0,
      "text": "In a petri dish, that&#39;s not that hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 413785.0,
      "end_time": 416254.0,
      "text": "but if you&#39;re trying to do it on a whole organism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 416254.0,
      "end_time": 418224.0,
      "text": "it gets really tricky."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 418224.0,
      "end_time": 421434.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s OK if you use something like blood or bone marrow --"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 421434.0,
      "end_time": 423685.0,
      "text": "those are the targets of a lot of research now."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 423685.0,
      "end_time": 425960.0,
      "text": "There was a great story of some little girl"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 425960.0,
      "end_time": 427636.0,
      "text": "who they saved from leukemia"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 427636.0,
      "end_time": 430334.0,
      "text": "by taking the blood out, editing it, and putting it back"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 430334.0,
      "end_time": 432869.0,
      "text": "with a precursor of CRISPR."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 432869.0,
      "end_time": 435689.0,
      "text": "And this is a line of research that people are going to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 435689.0,
      "end_time": 438266.0,
      "text": "But right now, if you want to get into the whole body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 438266.0,
      "end_time": 440434.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re probably going to have to use a virus."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 440434.0,
      "end_time": 442831.0,
      "text": "So you take the virus, you put the CRISPR into it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 442831.0,
      "end_time": 444561.0,
      "text": "you let the virus infect the cell."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 444561.0,
      "end_time": 446728.0,
      "text": "But now you&#39;ve got this virus in there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 446728.0,
      "end_time": 449440.0,
      "text": "and we don&#39;t know what the long-term effects of that are."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 449440.0,
      "end_time": 451732.0,
      "text": "Plus, CRISPR has some off-target effects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 451732.0,
      "end_time": 454717.0,
      "text": "a very small percentage, but they&#39;re still there."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 454717.0,
      "end_time": 458039.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s going to happen over time with that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 458039.0,
      "end_time": 460275.0,
      "text": "These are not trivial questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 460275.0,
      "end_time": 462939.0,
      "text": "and there are scientists that are trying to solve them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 462939.0,
      "end_time": 465249.0,
      "text": "and they will eventually, hopefully, be solved."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 465249.0,
      "end_time": 468907.0,
      "text": "But it ain&#39;t plug-and-play, not by a long shot."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 468907.0,
      "end_time": 471032.0,
      "text": "So: Is it really easy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 471032.0,
      "end_time": 475389.0,
      "text": "Well, if you spend a few years working it out in your particular system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 475389.0,
      "end_time": 477426.0,
      "text": "yes, it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 477426.0,
      "end_time": 479534.0,
      "text": "Now the other thing is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 479534.0,
      "end_time": 485917.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t really know that much about how to make a particular thing happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 485917.0,
      "end_time": 489306.0,
      "text": "by changing particular spots in the genome."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 489306.0,
      "end_time": 491497.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re a long way away from figuring out"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 491497.0,
      "end_time": 494364.0,
      "text": "how to give a pig wings, for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 494364.0,
      "end_time": 497252.0,
      "text": "Or even an extra leg -- I&#39;d settle for an extra leg."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 497252.0,
      "end_time": 498922.0,
      "text": "That would be kind of cool, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 498922.0,
      "end_time": 500482.0,
      "text": "But what is happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 500482.0,
      "end_time": 504856.0,
      "text": "is that CRISPR is being used by thousands and thousands of scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 504856.0,
      "end_time": 507252.0,
      "text": "to do really, really important work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 507252.0,
      "end_time": 512720.0,
      "text": "like making better models of diseases in animals, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 512720.0,
      "end_time": 517726.0,
      "text": "or for taking pathways that produce valuable chemicals"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 517726.0,
      "end_time": 522021.0,
      "text": "and getting them into industrial production in fermentation vats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 522020.99999999994,
      "end_time": 526022.0,
      "text": "or even doing really basic research on what genes do."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 526022.0,
      "end_time": 528975.0,
      "text": "This is the story of CRISPR we should be telling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 528975.0,
      "end_time": 532463.0,
      "text": "and I don&#39;t like it that the flashier aspects of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 532463.0,
      "end_time": 534243.0,
      "text": "are drowning all of this out."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 534243.0,
      "end_time": 538841.0,
      "text": "Lots of scientists did a lot of work to make CRISPR happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 538841.0,
      "end_time": 540484.0,
      "text": "and what&#39;s interesting to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 540484.0,
      "end_time": 545423.0,
      "text": "is that these scientists are being supported by our society."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 545423.0,
      "end_time": 546606.0,
      "text": "Think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 546606.0,
      "end_time": 550983.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve got an infrastructure that allows a certain percentage of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 550983.0,
      "end_time": 554984.0,
      "text": "to spend all their time doing research."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 554984.0,
      "end_time": 558998.0,
      "text": "That makes us all the inventors of CRISPR,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 558998.0,
      "end_time": 563490.0,
      "text": "and I would say that makes us all the shepherds of CRISPR."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 563490.0,
      "end_time": 565749.0,
      "text": "We all have a responsibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 565749.0,
      "end_time": 570010.0,
      "text": "So I would urge you to really learn about these types of technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 570010.0,
      "end_time": 572415.0,
      "text": "because, really, only in that way"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 572415.0,
      "end_time": 576791.0,
      "text": "are we going to be able to guide the development of these technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 576791.0,
      "end_time": 578747.0,
      "text": "the use of these technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 578747.0,
      "end_time": 583034.0,
      "text": "and make sure that, in the end, it&#39;s a positive outcome --"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 583034.0,
      "end_time": 586698.0,
      "text": "for both the planet and for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 586698.0,
      "end_time": 587914.0,
      "text": "Thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 587914.0,
      "end_time": 597914.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}